      "text": "物理末位（最早压入）的 Tuple (Item 0):0x1FD8 - 0x1FEF",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "物理末位（最早压入）的 Tuple (Item 0):0x1FD8 - 0x1FEF",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
    {
      "id": "g0Au9Z3F9icGEL5u-TNnC",
      "type": "text",
      "x": 803.3340502539198,
      "y": 3234.6000818119073,
      "width": 727.5597534179688,
      "height": 275,
      "angle": 0,
      "strokeColor": "#1e1e1e",
      "backgroundColor": "transparent",
      "fillStyle": "solid",
      "strokeWidth": 2,
      "strokeStyle": "solid",
      "roughness": 1,
      "opacity": 100,
      "groupIds": [],
      "frameId": null,
      "index": "b0L",
      "roundness": null,
      "seed": 834804001,
      "version": 718,
      "versionNonce": 2137999425,
      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": [],
      "updated": 1784099665231,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "text": "0x1FD8 - 0x1FDB (4字节)：ip_blkid (指向第 12 个子页面的块号) \nhex值为：00 00 01 00转小端序 0x01，十进制1，指向第1个page\n\n0x1ED4 - 0x1ED5 (2字节)：ip_posid (内部节点为 0)\nhex值为：FF FF，无意义，占位填充\n\n0x1ED6 - 0x1ED7 (2字节)：t_info (行信息与长度，即 18 00 对应 24 字节)\nhex值为：18 00，转小端序：0x18，十进制24，代表item11长度为24字节\n\n0x1ED8 - 0x1EE7 (16字节)：Payload (存储该子树外包框的 4 个 Float4 坐标)\n",
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 5,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "top",
      "containerId": null,
      "originalText": "0x1FD8 - 0x1FDB (4字节)：ip_blkid (指向第 12 个子页面的块号) \nhex值为：00 00 01 00转小端序 0x01，十进制1，指向第1个page\n\n0x1ED4 - 0x1ED5 (2字节)：ip_posid (内部节点为 0)\nhex值为：FF FF，无意义，占位填充\n\n0x1ED6 - 0x1ED7 (2字节)：t_info (行信息与长度，即 18 00 对应 24 字节)\nhex值为：18 00，转小端序：0x18，十进制24，代表item11长度为24字节\n\n0x1ED8 - 0x1EE7 (16字节)：Payload (存储该子树外包框的 4 个 Float4 坐标)\n",
      "autoResize": true,
      "lineHeight": 1.25
    },
